          transliteration: "grīvā mahastava mukhaṁ ca janastapastu phālaṁ śirastava samastamayasya satyam |\nevaṁ jaganmayatanō jagadāśritair- apyanyairnibaddhavapuṣē bhagavannamastē ||",
