          transliteration: "śataṁ kṛtatapāstataḥ sa khalu divyasaṁvatsarā-\nnavāpya ca tapobalaṁ matibalaṁ ca pūrvādhikam |\nudīkṣya kila kampitaṁ payasi paṅkajaṁ vāyunā\nbhavadbalavijṛmbhitaḥ pavanapāthasī pītavān ||",
