          transliteration: "aśītivarṣē samupētya mṛtyunā\ntribhiḥ sa dūtairyamarājakiṅkaraiḥ |\nbhayāturō nāma kilaitadarbhakaṁ\nprabhō nanāmōccaraṇēna nārāyaṇam ||",
