          translation: "There, Lakshmana, devoted to his brother, with auspicious resolve, built a lovely leaf-thatched hermitage using bamboo, timber, and beautiful leaves. Sita, ever righteous in conduct, arranged the household duties. Thus the three dwelt happily in the forest, united in devotion.",
