          transliteration: "tato bhavān dāvadahaṁ samantato\nmukhena pītvā sakalaṁ kṣaṇādiva |\nnimīlitākṣān punarāha bālakān\nvimocayadhvaṁ nayanāni bālakāḥ ||",
